Frida. The Swiss Army knife of dynamic instrumentation. Because who needs to recompile when you can just stab a running process with JavaScript? 🔪

---

## What Is Frida? 🎯

Frida is a dynamic instrumentation toolkit that lets you inject JavaScript into running processes on Windows, macOS, Linux, iOS, Android, and even QNX. No source code needed. No recompilation. Just point, shoot, and own.

Think of it like surgery on a live patient. You don't kill the process. You just modify its behavior while it's running. 😈

## How It Works 🔄

```
Your Computer (Python/CLI) → USB/Network → Target Device (frida-server)
                              ↓
                    Inject JavaScript → Hook functions → Modify behavior
```

## Installation 📦

```bash
# Install on your machine
pip install frida-tools

# On Android (rooted or emulator)
adb push frida-server /data/local/tmp/
adb shell chmod 755 /data/local/tmp/frida-server
adb shell /data/local/tmp/frida-server &

# On iOS (jailbroken)
# Install Frida from Cydia/Sileo
```

## Basic Commands 🚀

```bash
# List running processes
frida-ps -U  # USB connected device
frida-ps -R  # Remote device

# Trace functions automatically
frida-trace -U -i "open" com.target.app

# Spawn and attach
frida -U -f com.target.app --no-pause

# Attach to running app
frida -U com.target.app
```

## JavaScript Hooking Examples 🔥

**Bypass SSL Pinning (Android):**
```javascript
Java.perform(function() {
    var TrustManager = Java.openDynamic("javax.net.ssl.X509TrustManager");
    var TrustManagerImpl = Java.use("com.android.org.conscrypt.TrustManagerImpl");
    TrustManagerImpl.checkServerTrusted.implementation = function(chain, authType) {
        // Do nothing, bypass
    };
});
```

**Hook Crypto Functions:**
```javascript
Interceptor.attach(Module.findExportByName("libc.so", "strcmp"), {
    onEnter: function(args) {
        console.log("strcmp called with:");
        console.log("  arg1: " + args[0].readCString());
        console.log("  arg2: " + args[1].readCString());
    }
});
```

**Bypass Root Detection:**
```javascript
Java.perform(function() {
    var File = Java.use("java.io.File");
    File.exists.implementation = function() {
        var path = this.getAbsolutePath();
        if (path.indexOf("su") !== -1 || path.indexOf("magisk") !== -1) {
            return false;
        }
        return this.exists();
    };
});
```

## Frida Gadget (Embedded) 🧩

Embed Frida directly into an APK or IPA for devices without frida-server.

```bash
# Inject gadget into APK
frida-gadget -f com.target.app -o app_with_gadget.apk
```

## Objection (Frida on Steroids) 💉

Objection builds on Frida with pre-built commands.

```bash
# Bypass SSL pinning
objection -g com.target.app explore
```

## Common Use Cases 🎯

- Bypass SSL pinning in banking apps
- Dump decrypted data from memory
- Bypass root/jailbreak detection
- Extract encryption keys
- Trace API calls (malware analysis)
- Modify app behavior without recompiling

